        <updateDate>2021-03-17T16:13:19Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Presidential Pardon Transparency Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill requires certain information about presidential pardons and reprieves to be made public.</p> <p>Specifically, the President must publish the issue date, recipient, and full text of each pardon or reprieve granted.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
